  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT MAKING AN APPROPRIATION TO MERCY HOUSE ADULT AND TEEN CHALLENGE FOR THE PURPOSE OF DEFRAYING EXPENSES RELATED TO THE DEVELOPMENT OF IMPROVEMENTS AND ADDITIONS TO THE MERCY HOUSE ADULT AND TEEN CHALLENGE CAMPUS IN GEORGETOWN, MISSISSIPPI, THE PLANNED LOCATION OF THE MERCY HOUSE ADULT AND TEEN CHALLENGE SHORT-TERM DRUG AND ALCOHOL REHABILITATION CENTER IN LEARNED, MISSISSIPPI, AND FOR THE ACQUISITIONS OF AND IMPROVEMENTS TO MERCY HOUSE ADULT AND TEEN CHALLENGE THIRD PHASE AND AFTERCARE TRANSITIONAL PHASE RESIDENTIAL HOUSES AND FACILITIES THROUGHOUT MISSISSIPPI FOR THE FISCAL YEAR 2027."
